This paper is likely to belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) sub-category as it presents an execution framework for processing large datasets on distributed resources. It may also belong to the Databases (cs.DB) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories as it involves managing and processing large amounts of data. Additionally, it could be classified under Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) as it involves developing and implementing a software framework for distributed data processing.
